If your opponent doesn't have one,

310
00:33:02,416 --> 00:33:03,958
come back, and we'll loan you one.

311
00:33:04,041 --> 00:33:06,208
Play starts in 20 minutes.

312
00:33:06,291 --> 00:33:07,500
What's your rating?

313
00:33:08,250 --> 00:33:09,375
