00:34:54,500 --> 00:34:57,625
Uh, they arrange it by ratings
on the first round.

333
00:34:59,125 --> 00:35:02,375
After that, winners play winners,
and losers, losers.

334
00:35:07,083 --> 00:35:07,916
Good luck.

335
