401
00:41:26,000 --> 00:41:29,250
You play 30 games in USCF tournaments,
then wait four months.

402
00:41:29,916 --> 00:41:32,250
- That's how you get a rating.
- That's too long.

403
00:41:33,250 --> 00:41:34,166
I want to play Beltik.

